1862820000.text: "Importantly, SIS3 did not affect ERK1/2 phosphorylation in either TGF-beta1 or colchicine treated VSMC (XREF_FIG) supporting both the specificity of SIS3 and the functionality of the EGFR --> MEK and ERK pathway in the presence of SIS3."
